# Local HTML — external browser + GitHub Pages

When you create, edit, or share HTML (especially under `apps/website/`):

1. **Always run** `open "apps/website/<file>.html"` (or `npm run roadmap:open`) — not Cursor preview.
2. **Always include** both links in your reply:
   - Local: `file:///Users/hardiktiwar/Desktop/Tandem/apps/website/<file>.html`
   - Live: https://hardiktiwari.github.io/tandem-site/<file>.html
3. After edits, **push to `hardiktiwari/tandem-site`** (see `github-pages-html.mdc`). Do not deploy via `Sach1ng/tandem` Pages.
